{"tid":196850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死3隻]男酒駕載妻墮江齊溺斃　妻已有數月身孕","createTime":"2017-04-11T14:30:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T16:07:29.000Z","uid":32407,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aba7f982c8ef15df28144f9de6e30f03c09baa4d","tid":196850,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T14:30:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170411/bkncn-20170411050704257-0411_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170411%2Fbkncn-20170411050704257-0411_05011_001.html&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1W26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=79bd7ce0\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170411/bkncn-20170411050704257-0411_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170411/photo/bkncn-20170411050704257-0411_05011_001_01b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170411%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170411050704257-0411_05011_001_01b.jpg&h=725357fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n吉林市一名男子，前日凌晨喝酒後，開車載着已懷有數月身孕的妻子，由松江中路由西向東行駛時，衝破護欄墮入江中。警方接報後到場，成功將兩人救出，惟兩人終因溺水時間過長而搶救無效。警方事後在男死者體內驗出酒精超標，初步判斷墮江與超速有關，事故原因目前仍在調查。<br />\n<br />\n吉李公安消防支隊通報，事發當日凌晨，當局接到調度稱，松江中路天主教堂對面有私家車墮入江中，急需救援。到達現場後，救援人員從目擊者口中得知，出事的私家車由松江中路由西向東行駛，先衝破交通護欄及江邊護欄，再從人行台階駛入江中，車胎朝上地倒浮於水上。<br />\n<br />\n但由於當時正值水庫放水，江中的水位高漲，且渾濁不清，救援難度極大。救援人員即聯絡水上派出所、交警等部門，出動快艇開展救援，約十分鐘後成功從副駕駛座的位置救出一名女子；而駕駛座的男子因入水較深，救援人員無法在水中解救，只能先用吊車將私家車吊回岸邊，再將男子救出。不幸的是，兩人因溺水時間過長，終搶救無效死亡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0260b68ecc48efb999eeeab4a94a34493618cb1","tid":196850,"uid":25221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T15:41:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ac551428d50f770f49ad4c810942647e5d453a2c","tid":196850,"uid":31575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T15:45:07.000Z","msg":"triple kill"},{"pid":"fc2bb2b2931585460c9746e024d49edad5730a72","tid":196850,"uid":36069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T15:46:16.000Z","msg":"Stan <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"737a4b2c9132384c20871fe586427bfa22ad04b0","tid":196850,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T15:46:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b34ae0ff4a7e591791f50d163747a9c60e057609","tid":196850,"uid":21197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T15:48:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Stan <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都第一時間諗起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb35f299f5a0f047f8ca390291b82a59480d1839","tid":196850,"uid":65984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T15:50:58.000Z","msg":"警方接報後到場，成功將兩人救出，惟兩人終因溺水時間過長而搶救無效 <br />\n<br />\n同&quot;手術非常成功，但是病人死了&quot;有異曲同工之妙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15e2e31b5fd39f6793f80486a59aba79f958d0d7","tid":196850,"uid":26422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T16:07:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Stan <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都第一時間諗起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nShut up bitch! I m tryna talk!"}]}